nodes.text: Nala Aldel was a female Human who lived during the Galactic War between the Galactic Republic and the reconstituted Sith Empire. She made her living as a merchant for Binary Star Realty aboard Vaiken Spacedock.

The Reputation Vendor for Binary Star Realty on the Imperial Fleet, Nala Aldel and her Republic counterpart Maia Vefri were added to the video game Star Wars: The Old Republic in the 2014 Digital Expansion Galactic Strongholds.
